00:42:31.458 --> 00:42:33.830
to have the ability to do this.

00:42:33.830 --> 00:42:36.230
JUAN ENRIQUEZ: Well,
it's up to all of us.

00:42:36.230 --> 00:42:40.480
We tend to be
optimistic curmudgeons

00:42:40.480 --> 00:42:43.140
but, you know, it's
what we choose.

00:42:43.140 --> 00:42:43.640
Right?

00:42:43.640 --> 00:42:47.610
It's not just, oh my
goodness, this happened to me.

00:42:47.610 --> 00:42:50.020
There are consequences
to choices.

00:42:54.340 --> 00:42:56.580
AUDIENCE: So what
would happen if we

00:42:56.580 --> 00:43:04.780
