For example, you
have Lasik surgery

00:43:58.450 --> 00:43:59.760
because people don't
want to have glasses.

00:43:59.760 --> 00:44:00.450
You have Botox.

00:44:00.450 --> 00:44:02.450
You have all of these
things that were initially

00:44:02.450 --> 00:44:04.820
designed to treat
diseases are actually

00:44:04.820 --> 00:44:06.526
being treated for other things.

00:44:06.526 --> 00:44:08.400
And so aging and then
beauty, and then sports

00:44:08.400 --> 00:44:10.780
comes in with the growth
factors and things like that.

00:44:10.780 --> 00:44:12.155
AUDIENCE: And you
can give people

00:44:12.155 --> 00:44:13.770
blood serum of younger people.

00:44:13.770 --> 00:44:14.080
STEVE GULLANS: Absolutely.

00:44:14.080 --> 00:44:14.790
And--

00:44:14.790 --> 00:44:15.970
AUDIENCE: And also your own.

00:44:15.970 --> 00:44:17.490
You can donate now.

00:44:17.490 --> 00:44:20.590
STEVE GULLANS: There are many
ways-- so you go, I want health

00:44:20.590 --> 00:44:24.912
and then I want to not age, and
then I want to live forever,

00:44:24.912 --> 00:44:26.370
is basically what
it comes down to.

00:44:26.370 --> 00:44:28.500
And people appear to
continue to pursue this.

00:44:28.500 --> 00:44:31.730
Now, the technologies that
are going to come to be used

00:44:31.730 --> 00:44:33.360
are going to be more powerful.

00:44:33.360 --> 00:44:35.580
And it really comes first
down to safety and costs.

00:44:35.580 --> 00:44:37.850
When will they be safe
and cost effective?

00:44:37.850 --> 00:44:39.642
And at that point--
well, we need

00:44:39.642 --> 00:44:41.350
to have a debate now--
but at that point,

00:44:41.350 --> 00:44:44.300
the rules will probably change
in terms of how societies look

00:44:44.300 --> 00:44:47.790
at it, just as we have
rules around taking vaccines

00:44:47.790 --> 00:44:48.930
for the measles.

00:44:48.930 --> 00:44:51.560
It's not viewed as
a personal choice

00:44:51.560 --> 00:44:53.560
in many parts this country,
whether you actually

00:44:53.560 --> 00:44:55.330
get the measles or not.

00:44:55.330 --> 00:44:58.180
AUDIENCE: But I
would argue that it's

00:44:58.180 --> 00:45:03.170
a personal choice if you want to
