00:45:03.170 --> 00:45:08.740
and not have any children,
versus having children and then

00:45:08.740 --> 00:45:13.247
deciding to make room
for them on this planet.

00:45:13.247 --> 00:45:15.080
JUAN ENRIQUEZ: But see,
even your question--

00:45:15.080 --> 00:45:18.610
which is an interesting
