00:45:18.610 --> 00:45:20.410
from time.

00:45:20.410 --> 00:45:22.890
So for our grandparents
it was basically,

00:45:22.890 --> 00:45:25.750
marriage and kids
a few months later.

00:45:25.750 --> 00:45:26.422
AUDIENCE: Right.

00:45:26.422 --> 00:45:27.880
JUAN ENRIQUEZ: And
today we choose.

00:45:27.880 --> 00:45:30.470
You know, I'm not going to have
kids for the next three years,

00:45:30.470 --> 00:45:32.130
or even if I'm
going to have kids

00:45:32.130 --> 00:45:35.440
I can have kids and freeze
the sperm, freeze the eggs,

00:45:35.440 --> 00:45:38.580
freeze the fertilized eggs, put
them into a surrogate mother

00:45:38.580 --> 00:45:42.470
and have a child that is
born years after conception.

00:45:42.470 --> 00:45:44.860
And now you're beginning to
say, not only can I do that,

00:45:44.860 --> 00:45:49.020
but I can begin to do some
diagnostics on the genes

00:45:49.020 --> 00:45:51.540
or I can change
part of the genes.

00:45:51.540 --> 00:45:55.900
So there's a whole series of
really important questions that

00:45:55.900 --> 00:45:58.820
are going to change
and challenge us

00:45:58.820 --> 00:46:01.609
and our kids in ways that
we just can't imagine.

00:46:01.609 --> 00:46:03.150
None of us are going
to live forever.

00:46:06.120 --> 00:46:09.220
But we did double the
lifespan in the last century.

00:46:09.220 --> 00:46:12.810
And we're likely to double the
lifespan again in this century.

00:46:12.810 --> 00:46:15.500
And after that, as these
things accelerate-- right now

00:46:15.500 --> 00:46:17.910
we're adding about one year
of life per every 10 years

00:46:17.910 --> 00:46:19.260
we live.

00:46:19.260 --> 00:46:24.100
And as this stuff accelerates,
if life or consciousness

00:46:24.100 --> 00:46:27.460
becomes downloadable, then
you get some very interesting

00:46:27.460 --> 00:46:27.960
effects.

