00:49:52.430 --> 00:49:55.810
And the first point I
should make is, like coding,

00:49:55.810 --> 00:49:57.210
you can learn it as a child.

00:49:57.210 --> 00:49:59.110
Manipulating genes you
can learn as a child.

00:49:59.110 --> 00:50:01.539
These are basically recipes
you can do in your kitchen.

00:50:01.539 --> 00:50:03.330
And you can go to the
internet and find out

00:50:03.330 --> 00:50:04.320
what the-- we're
talking about bacteria

00:50:04.320 --> 00:50:06.020
that grow naturally everywhere.

00:50:06.020 --> 00:50:07.750
In the dirt, on your
kitchen counter,

00:50:07.750 --> 00:50:09.890
anything, and learning
how to manipulate those

00:50:09.890 --> 00:50:12.980
is not a huge technical change.

