We have not been operating at
a level of, basically, ones

00:50:15.460 --> 00:50:19.270
and zeros with ATCG and
higher-level programming

00:50:19.270 --> 00:50:21.325
languages effectively
are coming out right now.

00:50:21.325 --> 00:50:21.950
AUDIENCE: Yeah?

00:50:21.950 --> 00:50:23.020
STEVE GULLANS: These are
