00:55:51.060 --> 00:55:53.890
Now, if the clock was
400 per generation

00:55:53.890 --> 00:55:55.790
it's a different time
period versus 100.

00:55:55.790 --> 00:55:57.445
So right now the
operating number

00:55:57.445 --> 00:55:59.110
is 100 until we get more data.

00:56:03.590 --> 00:56:07.810
AUDIENCE: This talks
started out by emphasizing

00:56:07.810 --> 00:56:11.310
